author: Adam Loewy
title: Thursday’s prep volleyball results
text:
Thursday’s prep volleyball results Originally published October 1, 2015 at 11:03 pm Enumclaw's early lead, helped power their offense to a conference win and Monroe cruised to an easy three set victory. By Adam Loewy 
Enumclaw 3, Bonney Lake 1. 
Enumclaw took an early two-set lead to knock off Bonney Lake in a 3A conference match-up. Senior Barbara Becker shined offensively, recording 14 kills and three aces. Becker and senior Victoria Hernandez also dominated defensively, adding 18 and 24 digs, respectively.
